Detailed Description

Generates variable computation times, uniformely distributed between [c(1-d), c(1+d)].

Definition at line 448 of file load.hpp.

Constructor & Destructor Documentation

UniformCTGen ( Tick  cmin = CMIN_DEF,
double  d = DELTA_DEF 
)
inline

The computation times are variable, within [max(cmin, c*(1-d), c*(1+d)] and c is computed from the interarrival times.

Parameters
cmin(optional) minimum possible computation time by default is 1
d(optional) the percentage of variation. By default, is 0.1
